{"tid":1566881,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"[Johnny’s]Hey!Say!JUMP集中討論區","createTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:27.000Z","uid":296211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc5767c50a8e9c3deee5f7c8fd3b8d251be7ee4","tid":1566881,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:48.000Z","msg":"第一次出Post希望大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登真係冇乜J家Post 跳post得1個仲要18年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n適逢10月就有con睇！ 募集全體跳飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有黎緊17號抽蛋巡啊 <br />\n大家唔係放棄咁好嘅機會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以互相抽飛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOVhOOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOVhOOk.jpg&h=cc3ff9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Hey! Say! JUMP是日本的男性偶像團體，團員人數9人為傑尼斯事務所旗下團體中最多。於2007年9月21日成軍，並於同年11月14日發行首張單曲『Ultra Music Power』正式出道。唱片公司為J Storm。名稱中的「hey say」具有日語中「平成」的諧音，意指成員皆為「平成」年代出生。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">現任成員<br />\nHey! Say! BEST<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">藪宏太</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">高木雄也</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">伊野尾慧</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">八乙女光</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">有岡大貴</span><br />\n<br />\nHey! Say! 7<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">岡本圭人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">山田涼介</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">中島裕翔</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">知念侑李</span></span><br />\n<br />\n*出道時爲10人組合 森本龍太郎於14年退出J家<br />\n於16年加入ZERO與BLACK JACK"},{"pid":"86e9aef2d3f0cc6c48ad426d3fa19849787cd1c2","tid":1566881,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc5767c50a8e9c3deee5f7c8fd3b8d251be7ee4","tid":1566881,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:48.000Z","msg":"第一次出Post希望大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登真係冇乜J家Post 跳post得1個仲要18年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n適逢10月就有con睇！ 募集全體跳飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有黎緊17號抽蛋巡啊 <br />\n大家唔係放棄咁好嘅機會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以互相抽飛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOVhOOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOVhOOk.jpg&h=cc3ff9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Hey! Say! JUMP是日本的男性偶像團體，團員人數9人為傑尼斯事務所旗下團體中最多。於2007年9月21日成軍，並於同年11月14日發行首張單曲『Ultra Music Power』正式出道。唱片公司為J Storm。名稱中的「hey say」具有日語中「平成」的諧音，意指成員皆為「平成」年代出生。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">現任成員<br />\nHey! Say! BEST<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">藪宏太</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">高木雄也</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">伊野尾慧</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">八乙女光</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">有岡大貴</span><br />\n<br />\nHey! Say! 7<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">岡本圭人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">山田涼介</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">中島裕翔</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">知念侑李</span></span><br />\n<br />\n*出道時爲10人組合 森本龍太郎於14年退